## Overview

The Trust Payment system allows users to make payments towards their trust accounts. The system integrates with CHIP payment gateway and tracks payment history. Key features include:

- **Payment Initiation**: Users can make payments towards their trust accounts
- **Payment History**: View all payment transactions for a trust
- **Progress Tracking**: Track progress towards minimum trust amount (RM 100,000)
- **Multiple Payment Methods**: Support for online payment via CHIP gateway
- **Status Management**: Real-time payment status updates via webhooks

